Class ReinstatementBuilder

  • java.lang.Object
    • gw.api.databuilder.DataBuilder<PolicyPeriod,B>
      • gw.api.builder.JobBuilder<B>
        • gw.api.builder.NonSubmissionJobBuilder<ReinstatementBuilder>
          • gw.api.builder.ReinstatementBuilder
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ValueGenerator<PolicyPeriod>

    public class ReinstatementBuilder
extends NonSubmissionJobBuilder<ReinstatementBuilder>
    Builder for a reinstatement. Most common usage is 
       new ReinstatementBuilder(basedOn).createAndCommit()
    for a BOUND Reinstatement with the reason code TC_PAYMENT
